            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">15 December 1858 ¶  ¶ With refe to yr Le ¶  of 12 Decr ¶  I have the honor to intimate that the leave of absence for 3 weeks which you have requested to enable you to take a botanical journey to the S...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">58.12.15</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From John Moore</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 2718, unit 3, p. 475, VPRS 1187 outward correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">15 December 1858</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With refe to yr Le<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">With reference to your Letter.</p>
               </note> of 12 Decr<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">M to J. O'Shanassy, 12 December 1858.</p>
               </note> I have the honor to intimate that the leave of absence for 3 weeks which you have requested to enable you to take a botanical journey to the South Western parts of the Australian Alps is granted by the Chief Secy to date from the 17 instant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">sd J Moore</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Government Botanist</p>
         </div>
